description: The Cheese E Wagon constructed out of the mind of former Executive Chef for the University Of Pennsylvania, decided one day to establish his delicious idea of making gourmet grilled cheese sandwiches and go on a journey to the streets of Philadelphia. Crafting the best grilled cheese with complex flavors and best quality you will ever find in a heavenly cheesy meal that is made just for you. Track down the Cheese E Wagon for your next cheesy experience, enjoy!
name: Cheese E Wagon
